Usage: pandoc2review [option] file [file ...]
        --help                       Prints this message and quit.
        --shiftheading num           Add <num> to heading level.
        --disable-eaw                Disable compositing a paragraph with Ruby's EAW library.
        --hideraw                    Hide raw inline/block with no review format specified.
        --strip-emptydev             Strip <div> without any id or class
        --classic-writer             Prefer classic custom writer on Pandoc 3.x to be compatible with Pandoc 2.x
